text: Conocrinus is a genus of sea lilies in the family Bourguticrinidae, containing 6 species. ==Species== * Conocrinus cabiochi Roux, 1976 * Conocrinus cherbonnieri Roux, 1976 * Conocrinus globularis (Gislén, 1925) * Conocrinus lofotensis (Sars, 1868) * Conocrinus minimus (Döderlein, 1907) * Conocrinus poculum (Döderlein, 1907) ==References== Category:Animal genera
title: Conocrinus
